298
00:12:07,151 --> 00:12:09,451
Of course nothing would be found, right?

299
00:12:09,451 --> 00:12:10,951
Unlike the rubberband,

300
00:12:10,951 --> 00:12:12,751
there could never be something that won't get stuck by the ring,

